# Copy to terraform.tfvars (gitignored) for LOCAL runs, if you need to override
# the defaults. Terraform no longer manages app secrets/env vars — those live in
# wrangler.toml [vars] and `wrangler pages secret put` (see the add-env-var
# skill), so there is normally nothing to put here.

# account_id has a default in variables.tf; override only if needed.
